You are given the rank and salary scale of a company-
Rank - salary
  1-     2,50,000 BDT
  2-     2,10,000 BDT
  3-     1,50,000 BDT
  4-       80,000 BDT
>=5-       50,000 BDT

Now, take the rank as input from the user and print the salary of the given rank.
[If user gives input 3, you should print "Your salary: 1,50,000 BDT].